title: proporsi pessimum dan Espansi
abstract: Expansion in mortar or concrete could happen due to chemical reaction inside it. Some various proportion of reactives aggregate with non reactive aggregates were combined to get maximum expansion  in mortar. Mortar without combining aggregates was also made to find out its reactivity.  Mortar was cast based on JIS A 1146. Mortar specimens were cured in controlled room with  temperature 40OC dan Relative Humidity 100OC. The Results showed that when reactive aggregates were used in proportion 30:70 with non reactive aggregates then the expansion was maximum.
